DOCUMENTATION

This App calculates the repayment amount for a loan given the term, frequncy of repayment, and rate of interest.

Inputs:

Amount of loan : 
                            Default value = 10000,
                            min = 1000,
                            max = 100000,
                            step = 1000
                
                Please do not include currency symbol
                This app works for all currency :p
                
                
Loan term :
                            Default value = 2,
                            min = 1,
                            max = 10, 
                            step = 1
                
                Term is in whole number of years
                
Annual rate of interest(%) :
                            value = 5,
                            min = 1,
                            max = 100,
                            step = 0.25
                            
                Input only numbers . Please do not add "%" symbol
                Note: The interest used is the effective annual rate of interest
                      See https://www.investopedia.com/terms/e/effectiveinterest.asp
                
Frequency of repayment:
                            Options available are
                            "Weekly","Monthly","Quarterly","Half yearly", and "Annually"
                            
Output:
        The loanApp calculates the equal instalment payable at the choosen frequency
        that is required to pay off the loan in its entirety by the end of the 
        choosen term given the choice of loan amount and the rate of interest.
        
